What a day.

1122
01:11:20,401 --> 01:11:21,818
糟糕的一周。
What a week.

1123
01:11:22,111 --> 01:11:23,278
我告诉你，我要离开这里。
I tell you, I'm out of here.

1124
01:11:23,363 --> 01:11:25,197
墨西哥过客的方式之一。
One way to friggin' Mexico.

1125
01:11:26,366 --> 01:11:29,159
听着，我明天的行程。 桑德森的岛屿。
Listen, I got a trip tomorrow. Sanderson's island.

1126
01:11:29,243 --> 01:11:30,994
- 不，不，不。 - 哦，亲爱的。
- No, no, no. - Oh, dear.

1127
01:11:31,496 --> 01:11:33,956
是格林的钱，和我要的狂欢节。
It's green money, and I'm thinking of cutting across for the carnival.

